    Class and Description
    ClientBuilder
    Use this as a factory to create IDiscordClient instances
    DiscordException
    This represents an exception thrown when there is an error doing a discord operation.
    DiscordStatus.Maintenance
    This object represents a scheduled maintenance
    Features
    This represents feature modules that this api supports.
    Features.FeatureStatus
    The current state of the feature implementation SUPPORTED = Feature complete UNSUPPORTED = No implementation available DEPRECATED = Things may be broken and will get rewritten or removed entirely EXPERIMENTAL = Still a WIP feature, things are subject to change without notice READ_ONLY = Feature can only read the status of something without the ability to modify WRITE_ONLY = Feature can only change the status of something without the ability to get the status
    IDiscordClient
    Represents the main discord api
    IDiscordClient.Image
    Represents an avatar image.
